## Boundaries

### CAN Modify
- `src/**/*.ts`
- `src/**/*.test.ts`
- `README.md` (if asked)

### CANNOT Modify (without approval)
- `package.json`
- `tsconfig.json`
- `.env*`
- `*.lock`
- `.github/**`

### CANNOT Add
- New npm dependencies
- New dev dependencies
- External API calls not in existing code

